{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":23156,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"与我不同就排异呗，就这么简单个事","timestamp":1592892463,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23168,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我不反对。","timestamp":1592892505,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23181,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我不反对","timestamp":1592892567,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23183,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"您好，是A，mks主义不反同","timestamp":1592892571,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23196,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"B","timestamp":1592892624,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23206,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不反对，但也烦西方一些影视剧/游戏里动不动出来个lgbt，并以此当作zzzz","timestamp":1592892646,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23221,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 老末日2玩家了","timestamp":1592892710,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23224,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"初级阶段，发展中","timestamp":1592892720,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23226,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 其实本洞主自己是不赞同AD的\nD自然不用说，之前有正义人士贴了：https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QEiIbjgmuix29jdr3TBE1A\n但是A的话，中国古代好像并没有歧视lgbt的思想根源","timestamp":1592892722,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23230,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那，支持lgbt的人又是哪里得到的信仰呢（别说西方民主自由）","timestamp":1592892732,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23231,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"A是主导，官方价值观反对西方价值观体系，LGBT平泉运动的来源是西方价值观体系，因此支持官方价值观就会在一定程度上反对LGBT平权。","timestamp":1592892744,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23237,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"个人感觉没有必要让所有人都接受自己的一些偏小众的偏好，也没有必要整天宣扬，只要没人来干涉自己的偏好就行","timestamp":1592892788,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23251,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 不用追溯到古代。主要是农村、小县城、小城镇、小城市里有很多观念非常保守的人。我们国家整体的性观念就是非常保守的。LGBT面临的困境仅仅是其中的一个方面。","timestamp":1592892833,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23301,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"本国反对吗……lgbtq要平权那是国外有天主教把同性恋视为异类，我国古代皇帝里有龙阳之癖的不少吧","timestamp":1592892984,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23360,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"A的话...“不孝有三无后为大”不足以解释么？","timestamp":1592893193,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23383,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"从本土的一些蔑视性词汇也看得出来吧，比如二椅子之类的？","timestamp":1592893264,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23417,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 因为没有反对的理由所以不反对","timestamp":1592893373,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23690,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: \n在道德上，最宽泛的态度就是“别人如何不关我事”（极端化一点就是开车不系安全带撞死活该也是个人的事）\n但是在权利上，LGBT人群有着和主流人群一样的借助制度保护自己的权益的需求（例如，允许同性伴侣得到类似于婚姻的权利和义务的婚姻制度）\n洞主自己认为，比起解决“LGBT人群被反对者疯狂辱骂”的问题，解决“一个人能否给同性伴侣的手术通知书签字”的问题其实才是更根本的问题","timestamp":1592894387,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23799,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":3864,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 似乎有科学依据说，LGBT部分程度上是天生的\n所以我支持啊，这就好比有人天生不喜欢数学，有人天生内向，有人天生肤色较……较暗，这总不能反对吧","timestamp":1592894959,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":9,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3864,"reply":19,"tag":null,"text":"观 #3847 有感\n本国反对lgbt思想的根源是什么呢\nA. 本土（从封建社会乃至更早就开始的）的道德传统\nB. 天主教传统\nC. 老大哥带来的风气\nD. mks主义的要求\nE. 其他","timestamp":1592892418,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782582,"url":"","vote":{}}}